Root cause: `docker-compose.yml` had `./vast_challenge.db:/app/vast_challenge.db` but the database is at `backend/vast_challenge.db`. This caused the backend to crash on DB queries (though `/api/job_transitions` still worked since it reads JSON/CSV files, not the DB).

Changes made:
1. `docker/backend.Dockerfile` — CMD now runs `d3js.py` (has CORS + all routes)
2. `requirements.txt` — added `flask-cors`
3. `docker-compose.yml` — fixed the db volume path to `./backend/vast_challenge.db:/app/backend/vast_challenge.db`

